00:20:08.308 --> 00:20:09.342 position:44% line:83% align:start
[NOA]
Huh?

00:20:09.476 --> 00:20:11.079 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
[laughs] Catching on yet?

00:20:11.445 --> 00:20:13.581 position:19% line:83% align:start
Remember the abilities
you activated?

00:20:13.715 --> 00:20:15.850 position:35% line:83% align:start
Your Spying
and Destructive Impulse?

00:20:16.551 --> 00:20:18.119 position:10% line:89% align:start
Like a parasite jumping host,

00:20:18.251 --> 00:20:20.420 position:7% line:83% align:start
they were designed to transfer
over to the winner's Device

00:20:20.555 --> 00:20:22.322 position:33% line:83% align:start
in the event
that I ever lost a game.

00:20:22.890 --> 00:20:24.391 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Naturally, with this result,

00:20:24.525 --> 00:20:26.861 position:27% line:83% align:start
they transferred
