00:20:31.431 --> 00:20:32.232 position:33% line:89% align:start
[strap rips]

00:20:32.365 --> 00:20:33.500 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:20:34.936 --> 00:20:35.837 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:20:36.303 --> 00:20:38.238 position:35% line:83% align:start
In the end,
I didn't lose the game.

00:20:38.706 --> 00:20:41.075 position:16% line:83% align:start
And your cursed abilities
have infected you instead.

00:20:41.341 --> 00:20:43.845 position:7% line:83% align:start
There really couldn't have been
a more perfect outcome,

00:20:43.978 --> 00:20:44.879 position:33% line:89% align:start
could there?

00:20:46.681 --> 00:20:48.082 position:44% line:89% align:start
Well?

00:20:48.216 --> 00:20:49.851 position:5% line:83% align:start
Are you finally ready to tell us
how this whole mess came about,

00:20:49.984 --> 00:20:50.952 position:38% line:89% align:start
Akizuki?

00:20:51.351 --> 00:20:53.386 position:35% line:83% align:start
[NOA] This
was the most important thing

00:20:53.521 --> 00:20:54.922 position:24% line:89% align:start
in the world to me.

00:20:55.056 --> 00:20:56.356 position:38% line:89% align:start
Precious.

00:20:56.490 --> 00:20:58.025 position:7% line:83% align:start
I haven't breathed a word of it
to anyone.

00:20:58.159 --> 00:21:00.460 position:13% line:83% align:start
[NOA] But there's no sense
holding back now.

00:21:00.595 --> 00:21:03.330 position:19% line:83% align:start
After all, this may be
the last chance I get.

00:21:03.463 --> 00:21:04.732 position:33% line:89% align:start
Last chance?

00:21:04.866 --> 00:21:07.034 position:10% line:83% align:start
I actually am kind of smart,
you know.

00:21:07.168 --> 00:21:08.335 position:16% line:89% align:start
I got an incredible score

00:21:08.468 --> 00:21:10.571 position:16% line:83% align:start
on my first intellectual
development test.

00:21:10.705 --> 00:21:12.507 position:5% line:89% align:start
One of the best ever, they said.

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:14.441 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was even headhunted
for grade school

00:21:14.575 --> 00:21:16.043 position:24% line:89% align:start
here on the island.

00:21:16.177 --> 00:21:18.746 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'd say that qualifies
as more than "kind of smart".

00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:21.682 position:13% line:83% align:start
Although, it's pretty much
only the most elite candidates

00:21:21.816 --> 00:21:23.851 position:27% line:83% align:start
that get accepted
into grade school here.

00:21:23.985 --> 00:21:26.921 position:5% line:83% align:start
You see, intelligence and talent
aren't enough.

00:21:27.054 --> 00:21:29.624 position:30% line:83% align:start
You need to be
from a good family lineage.

00:21:29.757 --> 00:21:31.592 position:21% line:83% align:start
There was zero chance
a normal girl like me

00:21:31.726 --> 00:21:34.461 position:21% line:83% align:start
was ever going to fit
into a pack that pedigreed.

00:21:34.595 --> 00:21:36.063 position:21% line:89% align:start
Even though I tried,

00:21:36.197 --> 00:21:38.533 position:19% line:83% align:start
I could never stave off
the feelings of inadequacy.

00:21:38.666 --> 00:21:40.902 position:16% line:83% align:start
I thought that if I could
just stop being normal,

00:21:41.035 --> 00:21:43.271 position:13% line:83% align:start
that if I could be someone
exceptional instead,

00:21:43.403 --> 00:21:44.404 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'd belong.

00:21:45.006 --> 00:21:47.041 position:21% line:83% align:start
So, I worked as hard
as I possibly could.

00:21:47.175 --> 00:21:49.677 position:10% line:83% align:start
I made it into the top class
in my first year.

00:21:49.811 --> 00:21:52.246 position:27% line:83% align:start
And in my second,
I became a Five Star.

00:21:52.379 --> 00:21:53.815 position:38% line:83% align:start
Suddenly,
they were saying it'd be me

00:21:53.948 --> 00:21:56.117 position:16% line:83% align:start
who'd win the All-Campus
Elimination Battle,

00:21:56.250 --> 00:21:57.685 position:19% line:89% align:start
and become Eimei's ace!

00:21:57.819 --> 00:21:58.753 position:47% line:89% align:start
Me!

00:21:58.886 --> 00:22:00.955 position:16% line:83% align:start
And I wanted it so badly
I could cry.

00:22:01.088 --> 00:22:03.758 position:13% line:83% align:start
At last, something to show
for all the effort I'd put in.

00:22:03.891 --> 00:22:06.326 position:27% line:83% align:start
Something to show
that I was special.

00:22:07.228 --> 00:22:10.198 position:7% line:83% align:start
But you took that away from me,
Hiroto.

00:22:10.330 --> 00:22:11.331 position:35% line:89% align:start
All of it.

00:22:11.464 --> 00:22:13.333 position:7% line:89% align:start
You destroyed me in an instant.

00:22:13.835 --> 00:22:15.435 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
So then, is that why you went

00:22:15.570 --> 00:22:17.238 position:30% line:83% align:start
and made a deal
with this "devil" guy?

00:22:17.939 --> 00:22:20.440 position:19% line:83% align:start
[NOA] The Devil's name
is Mikado Kurahashi.

00:22:20.575 --> 00:22:23.410 position:7% line:83% align:start
Headmaster of District Twelve's
Seiji Academy.

00:22:23.544 --> 00:22:24.912 position:21% line:89% align:start
He told me to cheat.

00:22:25.046 --> 00:22:27.548 position:19% line:83% align:start
To do whatever I could
to steal Stars from you.

00:22:27.682 --> 00:22:28.950 position:13% line:89% align:start
He said if I pulled it off,

00:22:29.083 --> 00:22:31.384 position:13% line:83% align:start
he'd make all of my dreams
come true!

00:22:31.519 --> 00:22:33.120 position:21% line:89% align:start
I was so, so scared.

00:22:33.254 --> 00:22:35.556 position:21% line:83% align:start
[sniffles] Everything
was falling apart on me

00:22:35.690 --> 00:22:37.725 position:7% line:83% align:start
right when it should have been
coming together.

00:22:37.859 --> 00:22:40.228 position:21% line:83% align:start
Didn't you ever think
of standing up to him?

00:22:40.360 --> 00:22:41.796 position:24% line:89% align:start
This Kurahashi guy.

00:22:41.929 --> 00:22:43.297 position:44% line:83% align:start
[NOA]
How could I do that?

00:22:43.430 --> 00:22:45.833 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can't stand up
to a monster like him!

00:22:46.167 --> 00:22:47.500 position:21% line:89% align:start
I can't do anything.

00:22:47.635 --> 00:22:49.804 position:27% line:83% align:start
You'd be best off
just forgetting about me.

00:22:49.937 --> 00:22:51.339 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is probably the last day

00:22:51.471 --> 00:22:53.140 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'll ever get
to go to school here,

00:22:53.274 --> 00:22:55.042 position:5% line:89% align:start
the last time I'll ever see you.

00:22:56.143 --> 00:22:57.612 position:21% line:89% align:start
I know it's not much,

00:22:57.745 --> 00:23:00.114 position:24% line:83% align:start
but I'm truly sorry
for everything I've done to you,

00:23:00.248 --> 00:23:01.148 position:35% line:89% align:start
all of it.

00:23:01.481 --> 00:23:03.483 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
No way, not like this!

00:23:03.985 --> 00:23:06.587 position:27% line:83% align:start
And just who said
you could give up, Akizuki?

00:23:06.721 --> 00:23:08.256 position:33% line:89% align:start
But I can't.

00:23:08.388 --> 00:23:10.224 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's nothing I can do
to fix it!

00:23:10.358 --> 00:23:13.761 position:7% line:83% align:start
I mean who in their right mind
could have taken on that devil?

00:23:13.895 --> 00:23:16.130 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Heh. Yeah, that's your problem.

00:23:16.264 --> 00:23:17.464 position:21% line:89% align:start
Too busy looking down

00:23:17.598 --> 00:23:18.933 position:27% line:83% align:start
